snippet.title: [サテラビュー] Spriggan Powered BS ver. (Stage 3)
snippet.description:
Ahh, another peculiar ROM.

A previous ROM dump called "Spriggan Powered Prelude" exists. This new ROM dump seems to be headered "Spriggan Powered 1", but goes into Stage 3. I am very, VERY confused.

ALSO: this is a test of me using Shotcut to upscale my video rather than OBS.
